sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant BackendAPI
    participant GeminiAI
    participant Database

    User->>Frontend: Enters "Taxi 500"
    Frontend->>BackendAPI: POST /api/parse {text: "Taxi 500"}
    BackendAPI->>GeminiAI: Prompt("Parse: Taxi 500")
    GeminiAI-->>BackendAPI: Returns JSON {amount: 500, category: "Travel"}
    BackendAPI-->>Frontend: Returns Data Preview
    User->>Frontend: Confirms & Saves
    Frontend->>BackendAPI: POST /api/expenses
    BackendAPI->>Database: INSERT INTO expenses
    Database-->>BackendAPI: Success
    BackendAPI-->>Frontend: Success (201 Created)
    Frontend-->>User: Show Success Notification
